{"tid":1309314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[小心滲透] 唔好咁易俾人帶風向","createTime":"2019-07-12T06:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T19:31:03.000Z","uid":278893,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"738cb4298b341eb555ab7e319910a39e46a09118","tid":1309314,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"小弟一直係cd rom<br />\n今朝一開連登<br />\n見到好多posts都係咁散播失敗論 失焦論 <br />\n講如果再係咁搞地區行動 連儂牆<br />\n抗爭就會失敗 佢自己都會退出<br />\n例如係以下兩個posts<br />\n<br />\n自從１８區有連儂牆      抗爭運動已催向失敗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308153</a><br />\n<br />\n如 果 再 係 咁 我 唔 想 抗 爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308332</a><br />\n<br />\n我想講我今朝一開連登 真係有動搖同自我懷疑<br />\n究竟地區行動同連儂牆係唔係真係會對整場抗爭有負面影響<br />\n<br />\n直至我見到以下個post 我先醒覺<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我地一直做嘅野係啱</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n每日訓醒個風向都轉哂咁<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dhzudS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dhzudS</a><br />\n<br />\n我同意應該focus 係5大訴求<br />\n但係其實連儂牆都可以係今日至到21號期間keep 住大家道氣 令抗爭風氣唔好冷卻<br />\n(我立場係連儂牆唔洗守 撕一貼十)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我係到諗緊可唔可以組織堆人夜晚mon住連登<br />\n令果堆失敗論posts 唔好咁多正評同帶到風向<br />\n歡迎大家討論吓咁做好唔好<br />\n或者可以come up with 其他可能性<br />\n<br />\n(不過<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>最有效都係大家要意志堅定</strong></span><br />\n自己judge究竟每個post想表達咩)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做 不要分化 對準政權 21號見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4751f21ef6b33ece9526ee48bf73113df25124e8","tid":1309314,"uid":278893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"738cb4298b341eb555ab7e319910a39e46a09118","tid":1309314,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"小弟一直係cd rom<br />\n今朝一開連登<br />\n見到好多posts都係咁散播失敗論 失焦論 <br />\n講如果再係咁搞地區行動 連儂牆<br />\n抗爭就會失敗 佢自己都會退出<br />\n例如係以下兩個posts<br />\n<br />\n自從１８區有連儂牆      抗爭運動已催向失敗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308153</a><br />\n<br />\n如 果 再 係 咁 我 唔 想 抗 爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1308332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1308332</a><br />\n<br />\n我想講我今朝一開連登 真係有動搖同自我懷疑<br />\n究竟地區行動同連儂牆係唔係真係會對整場抗爭有負面影響<br />\n<br />\n直至我見到以下個post 我先醒覺<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>我地一直做嘅野係啱</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n每日訓醒個風向都轉哂咁<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dhzudS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dhzudS</a><br />\n<br />\n我同意應該focus 係5大訴求<br />\n但係其實連儂牆都可以係今日至到21號期間keep 住大家道氣 令抗爭風氣唔好冷卻<br />\n(我立場係連儂牆唔洗守 撕一貼十)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我係到諗緊可唔可以組織堆人夜晚mon住連登<br />\n令果堆失敗論posts 唔好咁多正評同帶到風向<br />\n歡迎大家討論吓咁做好唔好<br />\n或者可以come up with 其他可能性<br />\n<br />\n(不過<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>最有效都係大家要意志堅定</strong></span><br />\n自己judge究竟每個post想表達咩)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兄弟爬山 各有各做 不要分化 對準政權 21號見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb5a868e8ccb2a5a1addd8ab4db39f9bce08126","tid":1309314,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:38:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"61e3bfce3c3e0ef04c8a7e38af2193fe76fc146c","tid":1309314,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:18:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5289e8c3bfaf9146750f6f6f66b58160b54c21ad","tid":1309314,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba61909ce2d0aadccf559e4f4f9fc1107b8aaf0b","tid":1309314,"uid":278893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e2e09657080d6562f55fa11b74c9ca4f3515b189","tid":1309314,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoh